			<h1>
				<a href="http://werblog.com/2013/03/twitter-updates-2013-03-22-to-2013-03-28/" title="Twitter Updates: 2013-03-22 to 2013-03-28" rel="bookmark">Twitter Updates: 2013-03-22 to 2013-03-28</a>
				
			</h1>

			<div class="post-footer">
				29 Mar 2013 &nbsp;&nbsp;| <a href="http://werblog.com/category/uncategorized/">Uncategorized</a>
				
			</div>

			<div class="post-bodycopy cf">
				<ul class="ws_tweet_list">
<li class="ws_tweet">Just got a press release about an anti-Wharton protest over something most Wharton faculty aren&#039;t even aware of. <a href="http://t.co/kyCJboovFh" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/kyCJboovFh</a> <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/315067716975345664">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">The issue: A controversial Indian politician was dis-invited as a speaker to a student-organized Wharton conference after complaints. <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/315068304492466176">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">What a sad story, with lots of villains and no heroes. We all have a lot more work to do to combat sexism in tech. <a href="http://t.co/aUWCblNEdM" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/aUWCblNEdM</a> <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/315075418313068544">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">Congrats and good luck!! RT <a href="http://twitter.com/aprilrinne">@aprilrinne</a>: Woo hoo! Our new <a href="http://t.co/SXiGFbllCV" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/SXiGFbllCV</a>  is launched. Check it out and spread the word! <a href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23collcons">#collcons</a> <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/315096639767465984">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">Best wishes to my friend Julius Genachowski as he departs the FCC. Many accomplishments to take pride in! <a href="http://t.co/sZrDlfzo0k" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/sZrDlfzo0k</a> <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/315105658867433473">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">Closing in on 45,000 registrations with 10 days to go!  <a href="http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T</a> <a href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23gamification13">#gamification13</a> <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/315118578896609280">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">Finally appreciating that the phrase, &quot;when it rains, it pours,&quot; isn&#039;t just a statement about the weather in LA. <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/315125324906123264">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">Issues for the next FCC Chair: End of the phone system, Spectrum access, Net governance, Cybersecurity, Post-&#039;90s competition theory. <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/315139440030928896">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">Don&#039;t be a fool! On April 1, start my free <a href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23gamification13">#gamification13</a> course on using game design to solve problems. <a href="http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T</a> <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/315161703547543553">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">Next session of my free massive online course on using game design in business starts April 1: <a href="http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T</a> <a href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23gamification13">#gamification13</a> <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/315501697524965376">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">Curious how digital game design techniques can be used in business? My free <a href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23gamification13">#gamification13</a> course starts April 1. <a href="http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T</a> <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/315909635473276928">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">T Minus One Week to the next session of my free massive online course on Gamification! <a href="http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T</a>  <a href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23gamification13">#gamification13</a> <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/316229243744948225">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">Still time to sign up for the Coursera <a href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23gamification13">#gamification13</a> MOOC spring session, starting Monday! <a href="http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T</a> <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/316576026211782656">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">I&#039;m at <a href="http://twitter.com/LePainQuotidien">@LePainQuotidien</a> (Los Angeles, CA) <a href="http://t.co/7gvIERJ9vT" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/7gvIERJ9vT</a> <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/316951175574474752">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">Don&#039;t be a fool! On Monday, start my free <a href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23gamification13">#gamification13</a> course on using game design to solve problems. <a href="http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T</a> <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/316969869998452736">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">50,000 registrations and counting for my next <a href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23gamification13">#gamification13</a> MOOC session. Still time to sign up! <a href="http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T</a> <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/317314718807248896">-&gt;</a></li>
<li class="ws_tweet">Next session of my <a href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23gamification13">#gamification13</a> massive online course starts Monday. Please sign up and spread the word!  <a href="http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/VbinFvDy3T</a> <a class="ws_tweet_time" href="http://twitter.com/kwerb/statuses/317344086866669568">-&gt;</a></li>
</ul>

				
